// the body of the function calls the push method on colors, passing the 
// parameter color.
// When you invoke updateColors with argument colors, the function assigns
// the color parameter value undefined since the program cannot access the 
// global variable color. The function than appends value of color undefined
// to parameter colors. Since both function and global variable colors point
// to same array, the global variable colors now has modified value 
